{"title":"塞上行","authors":["光未然"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞上行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光未然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄风心上留"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（题苏蒙烈士塔）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂飚如狮吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振臂上高丘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇兵穿大漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼敌狼窝沟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红星指北斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华表出云头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望烈士塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄风心上留。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小注：狼窝沟在张家口以北，形势险要。1945年苏蒙联军助我解放张家口，曾在此痛歼日寇。最近我代表文联、作协参加张家口地区文艺工作者大会，于十月革命四十一周年之前一日，过狼窝沟，谒烈士塔。其时北风怒吼，山顶积雪未消，塔上红星，光芒四射。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张垣即兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（赠张家口文艺展览馆）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕一穷二白！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有钢铁巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄气概。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉夜战吐红烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了长城内外；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖出地下宝藏多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼成个黄金世界；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教江南大吃一惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同夸塞北。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有最新最美图画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成千成万诗才。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问杜甫、李白："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可敢登上赛诗台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比个又好又多又快？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张北行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（歌草原民兵）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来张北看草地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧草割尽我来迟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地高炉喷烟雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟高地阔觉天低。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风掠耳日偏西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何处声声有马嘶？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久闻塞北多良马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是骑兵操练时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上民兵意气豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男兵英武女兵骁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声号令风尘起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似游龙戏浪涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪在肩头刀在腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有精神马有膘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心跨上千里马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直飞东海斩狂蛟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原如今公社化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼铁炼钢炼兵马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战马俯仰如人意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉草拉犁拉矿砂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张北女儿木兰花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上飞腾如箭发；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下马投入钢铁阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰山里舞钢叉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马下工农马上兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何妨倚马写诗文？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有豪情马有胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揣诗纵马过长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞上风光日日新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新诗新画写新人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新人新事写不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马驮诗到北京。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}